condition.narrative: Finance Agreement :Article V, 5.01 (a) | Description :the Recipient has established the Steering Committee referred to in Section1.A.1 of Schedule 2 to this Agreement | Due Date :01-Dec-2013

Finance Agreement :Article V, 5.01 (b) | Description :the Recipient has established and staffed the Project Coordination Unitreferred to in Sections I.A.2 and I.A.3 of Schedule 2 to this Agreement. | Due Date :01-Dec-2013

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Sect. I, A (4) | Description :The Recipient shall within three (3) months of the Effective Datefinalize and adopt a Project Implementation Manual satisfactory to the Association to be applied in the implementation of theProject. | Due Date :15-Apr-2014

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Sect. I, B(2) | Description :In order to achieve the objectives of Parts 1 and 2 of the Project,MYVTE, through the PCU, shall, no later than three months of the Effective Date, enter into: (a) a Management Contract with each ofCCI-BF, ANPE and the Maison de l’Entreprise du Burkina Faso (b)a Service Agreement with MIT and (c) shall cause MIT to enter into aService Agreement with each of the communes. | Due Date :15-Apr-2014

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section II, A 1 | Description :The Recipient shall monitor and evaluate the progress of the Projectand prepare Project Reports, and shall furnish them to the World Bank not later than 45 days after the end of the period covered bysuch report. | Frequency :Yearly

Finance Agreement :Schedule 2, Section II, B 2 | Description :the Recipient shall prepare and furnish to the Association not laterthan forty-five (45) days after the end of each calendar quarter, interim unaudited financial reports for the Project covering thequarter, in form and substance satisfactory to the Association. | Frequency :Quarterly
